Instruments
===========
Below is the list of instruments included in this plugin

Actuators
+++++++++

* **DAQmx**: Analog output DC, Sinus, Ramp...

Viewer0D
++++++++

* **DAQmx**: Analog acquisition, Counting

Viewer1D
++++++++

* **DAQmx**: Analog acquisition




